 95→// ============================================================================
 96→// Timeout defaults (milliseconds)
 97→// ============================================================================
 98→
 99→/** Timeout for user-facing requests that require human interaction.
100→ *  2 minutes allows users time to read multi-option questions and deliberate.
101→ *  There is no UI countdown, so this must be generous. */
